channel.description:
World's Biggest features the world's biggest from around the globe!  

We will be releasing video every Tuesday, Thursday, Saturday and the odd Sunday from now until 2016!  Enjoy our new schedule!

This channel bring the biggest of everything.  For education and entertaining purposes, we will dive into everything from the biggest animals, sea creatures, humans, human parts, gangs, pimples, air plane crashes and disappearance such as Malaysia Airline MH 370, Biggest Hole, Real Super Human Powers, Bermuda Triangle Mysteries and many many more to come! 

 Subscribe to today and leave a comment for future video ideas.

For collaborations and business inquiries, please contact below.
